data.reasoningText:
It looks like `dotnet test` is only restoring/building but not running any tests. This is because with xUnit v3 (which uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform), the `dotnet test` integration needs special handling. 

On .NET SDK 11, the default runner might be trying to use Microsoft.Testing.Platform. Let me check if I need to set the runner explicitly in global.json. Let me try:

```json
{
  "test": {
    "runner": "Microsoft.Testing.Platform"
  }
}
```

